devdoc.title: Maintains a doubly linked list keyed by bytes32.

contains(LinkedList.List storage,bytes32.notice: Returns whether or not a particular key is present in the sorted list.

getKeys(LinkedList.List storage).notice: Gets all element keys from the doubly linked list.

headN(LinkedList.List storage,uint256).notice: Returns the keys of the N elements at the head of the list.

insert(LinkedList.List storage,bytes32,b.notice: Inserts an element into a doubly linked list.

push(LinkedList.List storage,bytes32).notice: Inserts an element at the tail of the doubly linked list.

update(LinkedList.List storage,bytes32,b.notice: Updates an element in the list.
